To run the server

- Install node
- Install required packages
  > npm install cylon-sphero
  > npm install director
- Run server
  > node sphero_server.js <port>
 (I'm using 8080 for all examples)

 To test examples
 - Install the Postman chrome extension
 - Using postman, import the collection under test_page/Sphero.json.postman_collection
 - Browse through the list for examples of requests that work with the server

 TBD: Write a simple html test page with buttons that will send the requests.